ai-kv22.5:1.1_0: There is no rebirth in the womb;
ai-kv22.5:1.3_0: He attains full awareness, mindfulness and lacks awareness.
ai-kv22.5:1.4_0: And you don’t keep on doing it.
ai-kv22.5:2.1_0: There is a penetration of the Dhamma.
ai-kv22.5:2.4_0: And you don’t keep on doing it.
ai-kv22.5:3.1_0: And there is no rebirth in the charnel ground,
ai-kv22.5:3.3_0: He attains full awareness, mindfulness and lacks awareness.
ai-kv22.5:3.4_0: And you don’t keep on doing it.
ai-kv22.5:3.5_0: The account of the three kinds of discussion is finished.
